{
  "id": "69b32cf1d994763bd8f2d027",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:技術者倫理",
  "created": 1773350159,
  "updated": 1773350193,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b32cf1d994763bd8f2d027",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:技術者倫理",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350159,
      "updated": 1773350159
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d0f00000000002849ad",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350159,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ae",
      "text": "やっほ〜！今日のテーマは「[技術者倫理]」だよ〜。なんか難しそうって思った人、挙手〜🙋‍♀️",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849af",
      "text": "でも安心して！ざっくり言うと「技術を作る人が、ちゃんと人のためになるように考えようねっていうルールとか考え方」って感じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b0",
      "text": "AIとかSNSとかゲームとか、ぜんぶ誰かが作ってるじゃん？そこで「作れちゃうけど、作っていいの？」って問題が出てくるわけよ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b1",
      "text": "じゃあまず、りか先生〜。技術サイドからどうぞっ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b3",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b4",
      "text": "了解。簡潔に定義する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b5",
      "text": "[** 技術者倫理（Engineering Ethics）]とは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b6",
      "text": ">技術者が社会・安全・環境・公共利益を考慮して行動するための倫理原則。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b7",
      "text": "有名な例としては、アメリカの技術者協会（NSPE）の倫理規定がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b8",
      "text": "https://www.nspe.org/resources/ethics/code-ethics",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849b9",
      "text": "要点は主にこの4つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ba",
      "text": " 1. 公共の安全・健康・福祉を最優先する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849bb",
      "text": " 2. 誠実に情報を伝える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849bc",
      "text": " 3. 利益相反を避ける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849bd",
      "text": " 4. 専門能力の範囲で責任を持つ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849be",
      "text": "つまり、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849bf",
      "text": "「作れるから作る」ではなく",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c0",
      "text": "「社会にとって正しいか」を判断する必要がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c1",
      "text": "技術者は、ある意味 社会に対する守護者だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c4",
      "text": "守護者って言い方、ちょっとカッコよすぎじゃね？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c5",
      "text": "でもわかる〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c6",
      "text": "例えばさ、AIとかさ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c7",
      "text": "めっちゃ便利だけど悪用もできるじゃん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c8",
      "text": "顔認識とかもさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849c9",
      "text": "防犯にはいいけど監視社会になるとか言われてるし。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ca",
      "text": "このへん、どう思う？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849cc",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849cd",
      "text": "（少し考えてから、穏やかに話す）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ce",
      "text": "そうですわね……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849cf",
      "text": "技術というものは、まるで鋭い刃物のようなものだと思います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d0",
      "text": "お料理にも使えますし、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d1",
      "text": "誰かを傷つけることにも使えてしまいます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d2",
      "text": "ですから……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d3",
      "text": "その刃を握る人の心の在り方が、とても大切なのではないでしょうか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d4",
      "text": "AIも、監視技術も、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d5",
      "text": "人を守る灯火にもなれば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d6",
      "text": "人を縛る鎖にもなり得る。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d7",
      "text": "わたくしは、本を読むのが好きなのですが……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d8",
      "text": "昔の物語でも、力を持った人の責任というテーマはよく描かれておりますの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849da",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849db",
      "text": "あ〜それめっちゃわかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849dc",
      "text": "能力バトル系のアニメでもさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849dd",
      "text": "「強い力には責任が伴う」ってやつあるじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849de",
      "text": "技術者もそれと同じって感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e0",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e1",
      "text": "概ね正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e2",
      "text": "実際、歴史上の事故でも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e3",
      "text": "倫理の欠如が問題になったケースは多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e4",
      "text": "例を挙げる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e5",
      "text": "スペースシャトル・チャレンジャー号事故（1986）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e6",
      "text": "原因の一つは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e7",
      "text": "エンジニアが「危険」と警告していた部品問題を、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e8",
      "text": "組織が無視して打ち上げたこと。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849e9",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ea",
      "text": "https://www.nasa.gov/history/challenger",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849eb",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ec",
      "text": " 技術的リスクは分かっていた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ed",
      "text": " しかし組織の圧力で決定が歪んだ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ee",
      "text": "これは技術倫理の典型的な問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f1",
      "text": "うわぁ……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f2",
      "text": "それはキツい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f3",
      "text": "つまりさ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f4",
      "text": "「ヤバいって分かってるのに、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f5",
      "text": "上司とか会社の都合でGOしちゃう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f6",
      "text": "みたいなやつ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f7",
      "text": "社会こわっ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849f9",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849fa",
      "text": "（少し胸に手を当てて）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849fb",
      "text": "そういう場面では……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849fc",
      "text": "とても苦しい選択になりますわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849fd",
      "text": "仕事を守るか、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849fe",
      "text": "人の安全を守るか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d1000000000002849ff",
      "text": "けれど、もしも事故が起きてしまったら……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a00",
      "text": "それはきっと、多くの人の人生に影を落とします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a01",
      "text": "ですから、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a02",
      "text": "勇気をもって「これは危険です」と言える人が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a03",
      "text": "とても尊いのだと思います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a04",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a05",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a06",
      "text": "補足する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a07",
      "text": "技術者倫理では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a08",
      "text": "[** 内部告発（Whistleblowing）]も重要な概念。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a09",
      "text": "組織が誤った判断をした場合、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a0a",
      "text": "社会の安全を守るために告発する行為。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a0b",
      "text": "ただし問題もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a0c",
      "text": " キャリアへの影響",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a0d",
      "text": " 組織との対立",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a0e",
      "text": " 証拠の問題",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a0f",
      "text": "つまり、倫理と現実の衝突だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a10",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a11",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a12",
      "text": "うわ〜〜〜",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a13",
      "text": "リアルすぎるやつだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a14",
      "text": "じゃあさ質問！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a15",
      "text": "AIとかゲームとか作る人って、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a16",
      "text": "どこまで責任あるの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a17",
      "text": "例えばさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a18",
      "text": "SNSが原因で炎上とかいじめとか起きたら、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a19",
      "text": "作った人の責任なの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a1a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a1b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a1c",
      "text": "良い問い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a1d",
      "text": "結論は単純ではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a1e",
      "text": "一般的には",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a1f",
      "text": "設計責任（Design Responsibility）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a20",
      "text": "という概念で考える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a21",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a22",
      "text": "技術者は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a23",
      "text": " 予測できるリスク",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a24",
      "text": " 回避可能な危険",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a25",
      "text": "には責任を持つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a26",
      "text": "例えば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a27",
      "text": " 依存性の高いアルゴリズム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a28",
      "text": " フェイクニュース拡散",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a29",
      "text": " プライバシー侵害",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a2a",
      "text": "こうした問題は、現在世界中で議論されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a2b",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a2c",
      "text": "https://www.acm.org/code-of-ethics",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a2e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a2f",
      "text": "（ゆっくりとうなずく）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a30",
      "text": "技術というものは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a31",
      "text": "まるで種のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a32",
      "text": "蒔いたときには小さくても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a33",
      "text": "やがて社会の中で大きく育つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a34",
      "text": "その木が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a35",
      "text": "人に木陰を与えるのか、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a36",
      "text": "それとも人を傷つける棘を生むのか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a37",
      "text": "それは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a38",
      "text": "種を蒔くときの思いやりによるのかもしれません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a3a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a3b",
      "text": "あや、今日ちょっと詩人モードじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a3c",
      "text": "でもいいこと言った！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a3d",
      "text": "つまりまとめるとさ〜",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a3e",
      "text": " 技術は便利だけど強い力",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a3f",
      "text": " だから作る人の責任デカい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a40",
      "text": " 会社とか圧力とかでヤバいことも起きる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a41",
      "text": " でも社会の安全が一番",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a42",
      "text": "って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a43",
      "text": "りか先生、採点お願いしまーす。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a45",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a46",
      "text": "採点する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a47",
      "text": "概ね正確。92点。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a48",
      "text": "補足して要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a49",
      "text": "技術者倫理の核心はこの3つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a4a",
      "text": " 1. 公共の安全を最優先する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a4b",
      "text": " 2. 正直で透明な情報共有",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a4c",
      "text": " 3. 社会への影響を長期的に考える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a4d",
      "text": "技術者は単なる「作る人」ではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a4e",
      "text": "社会システムの設計者だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a4f",
      "text": "だからこそ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a50",
      "text": "倫理は技術の一部になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a51",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a52",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a53",
      "text": "（やわらかく微笑む）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a54",
      "text": "とても大切なお話でしたわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a55",
      "text": "技術が進むほど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a56",
      "text": "人の心の優しさも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a57",
      "text": "一緒に育っていくとよろしいのですけれど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a58",
      "text": "未来の技術が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a59",
      "text": "誰かの涙ではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a5a",
      "text": "誰かの希望になりますように。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a5c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a5d",
      "text": "いい感じにまとまった〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a5e",
      "text": "ということで今日はここまで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a5f",
      "text": "次回のテーマどうする？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a60",
      "text": "「AIが世界征服する可能性」とか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a62",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a63",
      "text": "確率は低い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a64",
      "text": "だが議論の価値はある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a66",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a67",
      "text": "（くすっと静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a68",
      "text": "それも、少し楽しそうですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773350160,
      "updated": 1773350160
    },
    {
      "id": "69b32d100000000000284a69",
